<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF4FFCCFF02FAE8FDFC7345" blockId="8.[131,776,1364,1582]" pageId="8" pageNumber="121">
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF4FFCCFF02FAE8FE9270E6" author="LECOMTE H." box="[132,376,1396,1422]" pageId="8" pageNumber="121" pagination="99 - 121" refId="ref13173" refString="LECOMTE H. 1928 a. - Ebenacees nouvelles de l'Indochine. Notulae Systematicae 4 (4): 99 - 121. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 6463259" type="journal article" year="1928">Lecomte (1928a: 104)</bibRefCitation>
cited 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF4FFCCFE38FAE8FDA170E5" box="[446,587,1395,1422]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="121">Poilane 1863</emphasis>
from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF4FFCCFD1CFAE8FD3A70E6" box="[666,720,1396,1422]" name="Laos" pageId="8" pageNumber="121">Laos</collectingCountry>
, près de Sam Nuea” as the original gathering. Five sheets of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF4FFCCFD3FFA0FFF5670A5" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="121">Poilane 1863</emphasis>
have been located at 
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF4FFCCFE21FA28FE2470A6" box="[423,462,1460,1486]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15556" name="William and Lynda Steere Herbarium of the New York Botanical Garden" pageId="8" pageNumber="121" type="Herbarium">NY</collectionCode>
, 
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF4FFCCFE5CFA28FE0370A6" box="[474,489,1460,1486]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="8" pageNumber="121" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
and 
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF4FFCCFDA7FA28FD8D70A6" box="[545,615,1460,1486]" country="Viet Nam" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/tj07-dt2h" name="Institute of Tropical Biology" pageId="8" pageNumber="121" type="Herbarium">VNM</collectionCode>
. The specimen 
<specimenCode id="DBBD6356FFF4FFCCFF03FA4FFEEE7086" box="[133,260,1491,1518]" collectionCode="P" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="8" pageNumber="121" type="Herbarium">P00721522</specimenCode>
is designated here as the 
<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF4FFCCFD95FA4FFD9F7085" box="[531,629,1491,1517]" pageId="8" pageNumber="121">lectotype</typeStatus>
since it is the only sheet with Lecomte’s annotation and the best preserved with many fruits and a detailed label.
</paragraph>
